{"questionId":"9073600","questionHtml":"<p>An object of mass <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>m</mi></math> strikes a vertical wall horizontally at speed <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>U</mi></math>. The object rebounds from&nbsp;the wall horizontally at speed <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>V</mi></math>.</p>\n<p>What is the magnitude of the change in the momentum of the object?</p>\n<p>A.&nbsp;&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>0</mn></math></p>\n<p>B.&nbsp;&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>m</mi><mfenced><mrow><mi>V</mi><mo>-</mo><mi>U</mi></mrow></mfenced></math></p>\n<p>C.&nbsp;&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>m</mi><mfenced><mrow><mi>U</mi><mo>-</mo><mi>V</mi></mrow></mfenced></math></p>\n<p>D.&nbsp;&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>m</mi><mfenced><mrow><mi>U</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>V</mi></mrow></mfenced></math></p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>D</p>","meta":{"questionId":"9073600","referenceCode":"20N.1.SL.TZ0.9","subjectId":"46-dp-physics-last-assessment-2024","title":"An object of mass m strikes a vertical wall horizontally at speed U. The object rebounds from the wall horizontally at speed V. What is the magnitude of the change in the momentum ","paper":"1","level":"SL","questionNumber":"9","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 1]","breadcrumbLabels":["Core","Core","Topic 2: Mechanics","2.4 – Momentum and impulse","Core","Topic 2: Mechanics"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}